            <h1>Form Partials</h1>
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Through the introduction of the new form partials format, it gives you the ability to create forms in a simpler manner and gives you the ability to introduce dynamic content without using any javascript, therefore speeding up the form building process.</p>

            <div class="accordion">
